BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Dad's Garage 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260815T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260815T213000
DTSTAMP:20260707T000730Z
UID:occ-861@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Improv Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Improvisers from Atlanta's Dad's Garage make the whole show up
  from audience suggestions.\n\nPerformers from Dad's Garage\, Atlanta's lo
 ng-running improv comedy company\, build the entire show in the moment: sc
 enes\, characters\, and games sparked by whatever the audience calls out. 
 No script\, no repeats. Presented by Stage Door Theatre.
GEO:33.9447222;-84.3319444
LAST-MODIFIED:20260706T063411Z
LOCATION:Stage Door Theatre\, 5339 Chamblee Dunwoody Rd
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://ci.ovationtix.com/36385/performance/11804720/selecttickets
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Ripcord
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261003T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261003T220000
DTSTAMP:20260707T000730Z
UID:occ-1600@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:David Lindsay-Abaire's comedy of two mismatched retirement-hom
 e roommates and the prank war that spirals between them.\n\nDavid Lindsay-
 Abaire's comedy set in a shared room at the Bristol Place Senior Living Fa
 cility\, where the cantankerous Abby wants her sunny upper-floor quarters 
 to herself and the relentlessly cheerful new arrival Marilyn refuses to bu
 dge. What starts as a bet between the two women spirals into increasingly 
 outrageous pranks\, and each round unearths secrets both would prefer stay
 ed buried. From Stage Door Theatre.
GEO:33.9447222;-84.3319444
LAST-MODIFIED:20260706T063411Z
LOCATION:Stage Door Theatre\, 5339 Chamblee Dunwoody Rd
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://ci.ovationtix.com/36385/performance/11823389/selecttickets
END:VEVENT
